sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as FastAPI (Vanna routes)
    participant Agent as Vanna Agent
    participant Mem as ChromaDB memory
    participant LLM as LLM
    participant DB as MySQL

    U->>API: POST /api/chat (question, session cookie)
    API->>Agent: resolve user via JwtUserResolver
    Agent->>Mem: similarity search (DDL + training pairs)
    Agent->>LLM: system + schema + Q (stream)
    LLM-->>Agent: tool call run_sql(sql=…)
    Agent->>DB: execute SELECT (via AsyncMySQLRunner)
    DB-->>Agent: rows
    Agent-->>API: streamed chunks (text + data)
    API-->>U: SSE stream
